== 新闻报道及书评 ==
:1996年期间，戈茨在[[华盛顿时报|华盛顿时报]]发表中国政府向巴基斯坦政府贩卖核武器技术的报道<ref>[https://www.nytimes.com/1996/10/11/opinion/the-nuclear-gamble.html The Nuclear Gamble] {{Wayback|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1996/10/11/opinion/the-nuclear-gamble.html |date=20210308212636 }} "[[New_York_Times|New York Times]]" [A.m. Rosenthal] 10-11-1996</ref>。
:1997年，他根据以色列情报机构[[摩萨德|摩萨德]]提供的信息， 报道了[[俄罗斯|俄罗斯]]政府在[[伊朗|伊朗]]核武器将采取的援助计划<ref>[https://www.nytimes.com/1997/09/28/opinion/essay-iran-girds-for-war.html?pagewanted=all Essay; Iran Girds For War] {{Wayback|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1997/09/28/opinion/essay-iran-girds-for-war.html?pagewanted=all |date=20210308124141 }} "[[New_York_Times|New York Times]]" [William Safire] 09-28-1997</ref>。
:1998年，他在[[华盛顿时报|华盛顿时报]]上发表一篇报道，主要谈到美国向中共提供导弹技术，并要求其不得将此技术出售给伊朗和巴基斯坦等其他国家<ref>[https://www.nytimes.com/1998/04/10/opinion/on-my-mind-the-missile-business.html?pagewanted=all On My Mind; The Missile Business] {{Wayback|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1998/04/10/opinion/on-my-mind-the-missile-business.html?pagewanted=all |date=20201223063312 }} "[[New_York_Times|New York Times]]" [A.m. Rosenthal] 04-10-1998</ref>。
:戈茨2002年发布的新书 《The China Threat: How the People's Republic Targets America》中描述到中国的军事实力比美国所获悉的情报更为先进和强大<ref>[http://www.geoffmetcalf.com/qa/19668.html Is the 'China threat' real? Geoff Metcalf interviews famed national-security reporter Bill Gertz] {{Wayback|url=http://www.geoffmetcalf.com/qa/19668.html |date=20210224150748 }} [Geoff Metcalf]</ref>。同年，另一本新书 《Breakdown: How America's Intelligence Failures Led to Sept. 11》调查了2001年恐怖袭击之前，美国情报局的相关行动<ref>[https://www.nytimes.com/2002/11/20/books/books-of-the-times-a-catastrophic-failure-to-think-the-unthinkable.html?pagewanted=print BOOKS OF THE TIMES; A Catastrophic Failure To Think the Unthinkable] {{Wayback|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2002/11/20/books/books-of-the-times-a-catastrophic-failure-to-think-the-unthinkable.html?pagewanted=print |date=20210309033849 }} "[[New_York_Times|New York Times]]" [Sam Roberts] 10-20-2002</ref>。
:在2004年发布的《Treachery: How America’s Friends and Foes Are Secretly Arming Our Enemies》，书中谴责美国的盟友，例如[[法国|法国]]和[[德国|德国]]，为恐怖组织提供武器协助<ref>[https://www.cfif.org/htdocs/freedomline/current/in_our_opinion/bill-gertz-treachery-interview.htm Author Bill Gertz Discusses ‘Treachery: How America’s Friends and Foes Are Secretly Arming Our Enemies’] {{Wayback|url=https://www.cfif.org/htdocs/freedomline/current/in_our_opinion/bill-gertz-treachery-interview.htm |date=20210225182123 }} [CFIF ORG] 07-07-2005</ref>。
:2017年1月18日，戈茨在新书《iWar: War and Peace in the Information Age》发布会上表示，中国信息战将给美国各界带来不容忽视的威胁以及影响 <ref>[https://www.voachinese.com/a/bill-gertz-china-hack-security-us-20170120/3685879.html 华盛顿时报记者新书再掀中国威胁论] {{Wayback|url=https://www.voachinese.com/a/bill-gertz-china-hack-security-us-20170120/3685879.html |date=20200819143001 }} "[[VOA|VOA]]" [叶琳]01-21-2017</ref>。
:2019年9月12日，戈茨接受[[福克斯|福克斯]]商业频道采访，介绍新书《Deceiving the Sky: Inside Communist China's Drive for Global Supremacy》的同时也表明美国政府40年的对华贸易政策需要进行改革，我们要意识到[[一带一路|一带一路]]将会威胁到全球的经济以及军事平衡 <ref>[https://freebeacon.com/national-security/gertz-pro-china-forces-oppose-trumps-harder-line-on-trade/ Gertz: Pro-China Forces Oppose Trump’s Harder Line on Trade] {{Wayback|url=https://freebeacon.com/national-security/gertz-pro-china-forces-oppose-trumps-harder-line-on-trade/ |date=20200819143007 }} "[[Washington_Free_Beacon|Washington Free Beacon]]" 09-12-2019</ref> <ref>[https://video.foxbusiness.com/v/6085810962001/#sp=show-clips] {{Wayback|url=https://video.foxbusiness.com/v/6085810962001/#sp=show-clips |date=20200819143011 }} "[[Fox_Business|Fox Business]]" 09-12-2019</ref>。
:2019年12月3日，戈茨对于[[王立强事件|王立强事件]]在[[华盛顿时报|华盛顿时报]]上发表文章，报道指出中国军方在香港的走私行动，实质是为了获取美国以及其他西方国家的军事技术，同时，王立强在一份声明中描述这次行动将会干涉台湾大选以及破坏香港民主自由<ref>[https://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2019/dec/3/wang-liqiang-china-defector-australia-spills-commu/ China stealing U.S. arms and military technology from Hong Kong: defector] {{Wayback|url=https://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2019/dec/3/wang-liqiang-china-defector-australia-spills-commu/ |date=20201223123544 }} "[[The_Washington_Times|The Washington Times]]" [Bill Gertz] 12-03-2019</ref>。
:2019年12月24日，戈茨报道了中国正在开发的第三代潜射洲际弹道导弹“巨浪-3”的有关消息<ref>[https://www.guancha.cn/internation/2019_12_25_529436.shtml 美媒：中国又试射巨浪3潜射洲际弹道导弹] {{Wayback|url=https://www.guancha.cn/internation/2019_12_25_529436.shtml |date=20200819145803 }} [观察者网] [王世纯] 12-25-2019</ref> <ref>[https://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2019/dec/24/china-tests-submarine-launched-jl-3-missile-capabl/ China's test of sub-launched missile a threat to peace, retired captain warns] {{Wayback|url=https://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2019/dec/24/china-tests-submarine-launched-jl-3-missile-capabl/ |date=20210301045153 }} "[[The_Washington_Times|The Washington Times]]" [Bill Gertz] 12-24-2019</ref>。
:2020年4月3日，戈茨披露了新型冠状病毒的新线索，“一名武汉研究人员就在距华南海鲜市场3英里的低级实验室中分离出300多种蝙蝠病毒，并因接触蝙蝠尿液而自我隔离14天”<ref>[https://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2020/mar/30/china-researchers-isolated-bat-coronaviruses-near-/ Chinese researchers isolated deadly bat coronaviruses near Wuhan animal market] {{Wayback|url=https://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2020/mar/30/china-researchers-isolated-bat-coronaviruses-near-/ |date=20210327161657 }} "[[Washington_Times|Washington Times]]" [Bill Gertz] 03-30-2020</ref>。
:2020年6月4日，戈茨在接受Accuracy in Academia的专访时，介绍新书《How China’s Communist Party Made the World Sick》的同时也表明新型冠状病毒与中共有着密不可分的关联以及美国当局应当采取措施来调查病毒起因以及国际组织的内部问题 <ref>[https://www.academia.org/china-expert-warns-of-communist-chinese-coronavirus-deception/ China Expert Warns of Communist Chinese Coronavirus Deception] {{Wayback|url=https://www.academia.org/china-expert-warns-of-communist-chinese-coronavirus-deception/ |date=20210119131336 }} [Spencer Irvine] 06-04-2020</ref>。

